summary: Pokémon ask
title: Pokémon ask
body:
Alright, so I really like pokemon, and I really like yandere simulator, so long story short, I’m just going to…mash them together?

  • Send me a yan sim character and a pokemon (with the exception of legendary ones or abnormally large pokemon like Charizard) and I’ll draw them!

      Rules:

  • I’ll only do one pokemon per character.
  • one character per ask.
  • that’s pretty much it.

summary: Pokemon Sword & Shield Ideas
title: Pokemon Sword & Shield Ideas
body:
A hunted house (or castle) used as a gym, where a new ghost pokemon hides in the paintings. The gym leader would be a kid who talks about their deceased parents as if they are alive, and after the fight, one of the paintings would look at you even without any pokemon in it.

An area full of Flabebe and Floette, or perhaps a new fairy pokemon, deep in the forest. There could be stone circles in the forest, and maybe a new legendary pokemon could appear at the center of one of the circles.

Twin gymleaders, similar to Tate and Liza, one using defense based techniques and the other attack, having pokemon that could be found in a castle, like Golurk or Aegilash.

An underground area based on the Edinburgh Vaults with ghost and ground pokemon types. It could be where they gave a special event pokemon like how they gave Magearna in the Antiquities of the Ages shop in Hau'oli City.
